{
  "stem": "2533.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that particular Saturday, they had a lot of trucks loaded with furniture that the people wanted to get out to the country.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they didn't manage to get away because they didn't know it was going to be such a destructive air raid.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they couldn't even get out the next day from Frankfurt, because every road was damaged.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And before that, they told them to get out because they're going to bombard Frankfurt, but they didn't tell when.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Leaflets they threw down from a plane.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But all the civilians and the children, whatever wanted to get away to get out of Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But they didn't listen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They thought it was just to frighten them or something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And it happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "For three days and nights, the English at nighttime, the Americans in daytime.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then Frankfurt was-- wasn't anymore Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "One street was left standing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "The big big blocks of houses-- it wasn't houses like units.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were camouflaged.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were painted like trees.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that was-- the town was [NON-ENGLISH], and the street was called Rothschild Street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And later on, when the Americans came, they had the headquarters, the military headquarters in Frankfurt, was in those buildings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The last ones left, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Only Hildemann was there with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mrs.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Hildemann and Peter was in the country.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after it finished, we just got out, back to the country.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were still all in one piece.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But everything was-- somehow we got out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then when we came back, he started to build a house back again, but I stayed with the boy in the country.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
